news.title: Rajasthan HC issues status quo orders on sealing of 19 commercial sites in Walled City
news.para: The orders were issued by a division bench of Chief Justice MM Shrivastava and Justice Bhuvan Goyal on an application filed by the operators of these commercial complexes.

news.title: South City Mall-Blackstone deal 'speculative', no urgency to clinch sale: Consortium partner
news.para: "It has been receiving offers from various funds, including Blackstone, Brookfield, Canadian Pension Fund, and Singapore's Temasek since 2020," a significant consortium partner who wished not to be quoted told PTI.

news.title: About 18 million sq ft area needed in 4-5 years for data centres: Smriti Irani
news.para: Irani, the former Union Minister, also spoke about the growing number of Global Capabilities Centres (GCCs) across major cities in India and beyond.

news.title: Kolkata civic body relaxes building rules for owners of small plots
news.para: The relaxations will be given to those who possess plots of 300 sq ft to 2,100 sq ft. Using this unique scheme, owners of small plots — even those measuring between300 and 450 square feet — will now be able to construct a three-storey building, said mayor Firhad Hakim.

news.title: Ludhiana civic body seals unauthorised shops in Model Town extension area
news.para: On reports of alleged illegal construction in Raghunath Enclave, MC building branch officials said they inspected the site but found no illegal structures there.

news.title: Only two lakh PMAY-U homes target met in decade in Maharashtra: State economic survey
news.para: Of these, 2.04 lakh units have been completed and groundwork started for 3.78 lakh dwelling units for the economically weaker section (EWS).

news.title: Delay in funds holds up structural audits in 20 housing societies in Gurugram
news.para: The department of town and country planning (DTCP) has been issuing notices to builders and RWAs for over a year, but no action has been taken.

news.title: China's Evergrande Property Services eyes up to 37% decline in annual profit in 2024
news.para: In early January, a Guangzhou city court ordered the firm's parent China Evergrande to repay pledge guarantees on deposit certificates totalling 13.4 billion yuan ($1.85 billion).

news.title: SC agrees to hear CBI plea against bail to DHFL's ex-promoter
news.para: During the arguments in the apex court, additional solicitor general S V Raju, representing the CBI, said Wadhawan suffered from no serious medical ailments and huge amounts of money were siphoned off in the case.

news.title: SC refuses status quo on Dharavi redevelopment
news.para: The high court had cleared the decks for redevelopment of the slums in Dharavi and upheld the tender awarded to the Adani Group for the project, ruling there was no "arbitrariness, unreasonableness or perversity" in the decision.

news.title: Trichy corporation forms climate action plan committee
news.para: Officials said transport, residential buildings, waste management, and street lighting emit large amounts of greenhouse gas (GHGs) in the city.

news.title: Blackstone raises $8 billion in its latest real estate debt fund
news.para: The fund - Blackstone Real Estate Debt Strategies V - will be active in North America, Europe and Australia and make loans and buy existing loans, according to the company.

news.title: SC seeks compliance report on Amrapali Group cases
news.para: The top court has from time to time passed a slew of directions and orders to assuage the grievances of the hassled home buyers of over 45,000 flats in different projects of the group.

news.title: UK's FCA to make mortgages more accessible
news.para: The finance watchdog will launch a call for evidence on different methods of stress testing as part of an effort to simplify mortgage approval regulations.

news.title: Ambuja Cements to invest Rs 2,500 crore in building cement and clinker carriers
news.para: A 38,500-tonne capacity Handymax cement carrier costs about Rs 400 crore to build from scratch, while a 9,200-tonne capacity clinker carrier will cost about Rs 200 crore each.

news.title: BNP Paribas leases office space in Mumbai at Rs 811 per sq ft per month
news.para: Industry experts note that despite global economic fluctuations, marquee transactions such as this underscore the resilience of India’s commercial real estate market.

news.title: NDMC attaches properties in Delhi's Gole and Khan markets over non-payment of tax
news.para: Meanwhile, three tax collection counters have been designated at Shaheed Bhagat Singh Place in Gole Market, Palika Bhawan in RK Puram, and Palika Kendra in Sansad Marg.

news.title: House prices in UK dip unexpectedly in February: Halifax data
news.para: House prices slipped 0.1% month-on-month in February, after rising by a revised 0.6% in January, and were below all forecasts in a Reuters poll of economists.

news.title: Thane civic body presents Rs 5,645 crore budget for 2025-26
news.para: The civic body expects to garner Rs 841.58 crore from property and other taxes, Rs 650.8 crore from development charges and Rs 1,441.79 crore through GST and other grants.

news.title: Telangana high court halts land acquisition in Lagacherla and Hakimpet
news.para: Apart from suspending the ongoing land acquisition order, the judge sought counters from the state, revenue department and land acquisition authorities by April 7.
